      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 78.1 - 老子 78.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 78.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天下莫柔弱於水，而攻堅強者，莫之能勝，其無以易之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There is nothing in the world more soft and weak than water, and yet for attacking things that are firm and strong there is nothing that can take precedence of it;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
