      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天下莫不知莫能行。是以聖人云﹕「受國之垢，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Every one in the world knows that the soft overcomes the hard, and the weak the strong, but no one is able to carry it out in practice. Therefore a sage has said,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
